{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a703fd2b00","title":"在郑州会议上的讲话（六）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2dde24e051","index":0,"year":1959,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"a703fd2b00","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958-1960卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"479891defc","type":"title","text":"在郑州会议上的讲话（六）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e28f538a73","type":"paragraph","text":"什么叫建设社会主义，集中表现。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90c8a2cc52","type":"paragraph","text":"集体所有制和全民所有制要不要一条线？还是要一条线的。斯大林同志划了一条线，指出三个条件，先决条件，这是对的，缺点讲得不太具体，四十条中提得就比较具体了。许多问题斯大林没提到：并举、全党全民办工业、群众运动、政治挂帅、整风","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"23d21be3bd","type":"paragraph","text":"城市人民公社问题很复杂，不要怕慢，但要采取积极态度。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69248e7c82","type":"paragraph","text":"对农民问题：大跃进时对农民积极性估计不足，大跃进以来仍是农民问题，过高地估计了农民，究竟是鞍钢是老大哥呢？还是徐水是老大哥呢？还是工人阶级，鞍钢是老大哥。有些“理论家”一遇到实际问题就打折扣，他们就回避资本主义留下来的东西：商品生产和价值规律，问题在于怎么认识，看对我们的社会主义建设有没有好处？有好处就利用，为我们服务。要利用商品生产、价值规律。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a15ec24c2","type":"paragraph","text":"过早宣传全民所有，国家就要调拨，是实质上剥夺了农民，农民会不高兴的，谁高兴这样做呢？台湾，唯恐天下不乱","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"218ea77067","type":"paragraph","text":"公社也可以办赢利较多的工业。（斯大林不敢把拖拉机交给农庄）","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aa94fce4ae","type":"paragraph","text":"有人把农民当成工人，这不对。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cedaaa7287","type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕商品生产，问题要看同什么样的经济相联系","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a066744490","type":"paragraph","text":"不能把人与人的关系看成是父子关系，而是平等关系。破除不平等，但仍然要有差别。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"141d38a254","type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁、机械、电很重要，林业很重要，也要成为根本问题之一","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"07158b82f6","type":"paragraph","text":"价值法则不起调节作用，只是计算工具。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e83caf9ed7","type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社实行了全民所有制不算共产主义。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"271b7824c2","type":"paragraph","text":"苦战三年，再过十二年就可过渡到共产主义。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":314,"end":313}},"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"06e1f0a668","type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁、炼、机械、电很重要，林业很重要，也要成为根本问题之一。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ad1168162","type":"paragraph","text":"城市人民公社问题很复杂，不要怕慢，但要采取积极态度。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"a703fd2b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"146bb01187","type":"paragraph","text":"公社也可以办赢利较多的工业。（斯大林不敢把拖拉机